{
  "id": "019ce540-1f08-7491-a065-13da6eaf1c73",
  "content": "# Temporal History Explorer — Implementation Record (2026-03-13)\n\n## What was built\nAgent B implemented the Temporal History Explorer as a new \"History\" tab in the corvia dashboard (tools/corvia-dashboard). This is Tier 2, Feature #5 from the Dashboard Feature Roadmap.\n\n## Backend changes (repos/corvia/crates/corvia-server/src/dashboard/mod.rs)\n- Added `GET /api/dashboard/entries/{entry_id}` — returns a single entry's full detail (id, content, scope_id, recorded_at, valid_from, valid_to, superseded_by, metadata)\n- Added `GET /api/dashboard/entries/{entry_id}/history` — returns the supersession chain via `state.temporal.history()` as `{ entry_id, chain: [...], count }` where each chain entry includes is_current flag\n- Uses `TemporalStore::history()` trait (not QueryableStore) and `QueryableStore::get()` for entry detail\n\n## Frontend changes\n- `types.ts`: Added EntryDetail, HistoryEntry, HistoryResponse interfaces\n- `api.ts`: Added fetchEntryDetail() and fetchEntryHistory() functions\n- `Layout.tsx`: Added \"history\" to Tab type union, added History tab, renders HistoryView component\n- `HistoryView.tsx` (new): Full temporal history explorer with:\n  - Entry UUID lookup bar\n  - Vertical timeline showing supersession chain with version numbers, timestamps, content previews\n  - Time travel slider (range input) to navigate versions\n  - LCS-based diff view with compare version dropdowns\n  - Entry detail card with full metadata and content display\n  - Uses lavender color from design system as primary accent\n\n## Design decisions\n- Used `state.temporal` (TemporalStore trait) for history, not `state.store` (QueryableStore)\n- LCS diff algorithm implemented inline (no external dependency) for accurate line-by-line diffs\n- Lavender accent color chosen to differentiate from other tabs (sky=RAG, mint=agents, gold=traces)\n- Dev server runs on port 8024 to avoid conflict with main dashboard (8021) and Agent A (8023)\n\n## Coordination with Agent A\n- Did NOT touch GraphView.tsx, traits.rs, or any kernel files per TASK.md constraints\n- Shared files (Layout.tsx, api.ts, types.ts) have additive-only changes for clean merge",
  "source_version": "feature/temporal-history",
